name: Timmy Turner Dies in a Swamp
name_original: Timmy Turner Dies in a Swamp
description:
Uh oh! 

Timmy Turner's oddparents have turned evil and are making a vacant swamp their home. They are terrorizing any visitors that come near them or their territory. It's up to you to stop the victim numbers from rising. 

You play as Timmy, a boy who wants his oddparents dead.  You ride to the deserted swamp with a bunch of weapons only to find out that they weren't loaded. You must find another way to take them out. Can you do it?
